data.description: Welcome to your new home in the desirable Lamplight Manor neighborhood of Virginia Beach! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch home offers 1,777 sqft of comfortable living space. Convenience is key with this centrally located property - you'll have easy access to major highways, bases, public transportation, and shopping. Plus, the beach is just a short 10 minute drive away!Step inside and you'll notice the home has been meticulously maintained, with new carpet installed in 3 of the bedrooms and new laminate flooring in the bathrooms. The spacious yard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, with plenty of room for kids and pets to play.Don't miss your chance to own this gem of a home. Schedule your private showing today and start living the Virginia Beach lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
